reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 3, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I was happy with these. I have 3 kids, ages 2-8 and bought these for a road trip. The alternative was headphones that were this price or more for only 1 set, times 3. Which my kids would have also broken and/or lost because they are super hard on everything. The two year old ripped the cord out of the headset of one pair. Another pair the interior speaker came dislodged but I was able to open up the headphones and fix it. They are very comfortable, very flexible, and we've had no issues from normal use. I prefer to have cheap ones I don't have to worry about rather than $30 ones I'm paranoid about. I like them so much I'm purchasing another set to have more backups.
